high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter next to the stove on the right.
Pick up the brown bowl from the right side of the counter.
Turn around and walk to the black fridge.
Put the bowl inside the fridge on the top right shelf, chill it, remove it and close the doors.
Turn around and walk to the microwave on the counter ahead.
Put the chilled bowl inside the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled bowl in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to to the counter to the left of the oven.
Pick up the wooden bowl off of the counter.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the wooden bowl inside then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the now chilled wooden bowl then close the door.
Turn right and walk over to the microwave on the counter.
Put the chilled wooden bowl into the microwave then close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled wooden bowl in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the left of the stove.
Pick up the tan bowl on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the bowl in the fridge to the left of the black mug. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn around and veer left to the microwave.
Place the bowl in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled bowl in a microwave.
